# ERP Workspace Unsaved Form Draft Preservation

Phase: ERP GLOBAL UI.4E.2

## Rules

1. All `ERPRecordWorkspaceForm` implementations MUST use `useWorkspaceFormDraft`.
2. Switching workspace tabs MUST NOT clear dirty unsaved form values.
3. Opening another menu or workspace tab MUST NOT clear dirty unsaved form values.
4. Unsaved form drafts are **in-memory only** ŌĆö stored in `WorkspaceDraftProvider` useRef Map.
5. Do NOT store unsaved form field values in `localStorage` or `sessionStorage`.
6. Sensitive fields in `DRAFT_FIELD_DENYLIST` MUST never enter the draft store.
7. ALL `defaultValue` props in workspace forms MUST use `getDraftDefault(fieldName, serverFallback)`.
8. Controlled combobox/select values MUST initialize from `getDraftDefault()` in `useState(() => ...)`.
9. Controlled combobox/select `onChange` MUST call `writeDraftField(fieldName, value)`.
10. `clearDraft()` MUST run after successful save, save-and-close, or discard.
11. User/auth password fields (`temporary_password`, `password`, etc.) MUST NEVER be drafted.
12. The form element MUST have `onInput={syncDraft} onChange={syncDraft}` for automatic capture.

## Standard Hook Usage

```tsx
import { useWorkspaceFormDraft } from "@/hooks/use-workspace-form-draft";

const FORM_ID = "my-workspace-form";

export function MyWorkspaceForm({ record, mode }) {
  const isViewing = mode === "view";

  const { getDraftDefault, getDraftBoolean, syncDraft, writeDraftField, clearDraft } =
    useWorkspaceFormDraft({ formId: FORM_ID, enabled: !isViewing });

  // Controlled state ŌĆö initialize from draft
  const [countryId, setCountryId] = useState<number | null>(() => {
    const d = getDraftDefault("country_id", "");
    return d ? Number(d) : record?.country_id ?? null;
  });

  const handleSave = async () => {
    const result = await saveAction(data);
    if (result.success) {
      clearDraft();   // ŌåÉ clear draft on success
      resetDirty();
      toast.success("Saved");
      return true;
    }
    return false;     // ŌåÉ do NOT clear draft on failure
  };

  return (
    <ERPRecordWorkspaceForm ...>
      <form id={FORM_ID} onInput={syncDraft} onChange={syncDraft} onSubmit={...}>
        <Input
          name="display_name"
          defaultValue={getDraftDefault("display_name", record?.display_name ?? "")}
        />
        <CountrySelect
          value={countryId}
          onValueChange={(v) => {
            setCountryId(v);
            writeDraftField("country_id", v ?? "");
          }}
        />
      </form>
    </ERPRecordWorkspaceForm>
  );
}
```

## Draft Key Format

```
draft:tab:{activeTabId}:{formId}
```

## Sensitive Field Denylist

All of the following (case-insensitive, also matched as substrings):
`password`, `temporary_password`, `confirm_password`, `token`, `access_token`, `refresh_token`,
`api_key`, `secret`, `client_secret`, `otp`, `pin`, `file`, `attachment`, `bank_account_number`,
`account_number`, `iban`, `emirates_id`, `passport_number`

## Lifecycle

- **Mount with draft** ŌåÆ restore `defaultValue` from draft, restore dirty indicator
- **User types** ŌåÆ `onInput`/`onChange` ŌåÆ debounced `snapshotFormData` ŌåÆ patch draft store
- **Controlled change** ŌåÆ `writeDraftField(name, value)` ŌåÆ write single field
- **Tab switch** ŌåÆ component unmounts; draft persists in memory
- **Tab return** ŌåÆ component remounts; `getDraftDefault` restores values; dirty indicator restored
- **Save success** ŌåÆ `clearDraft()` ŌåÆ `resetDirty()`
- **Tab close (clean)** ŌåÆ `clearDraftsForTab(tabId)` in workspace provider
- **Tab close (discard)** ŌåÆ `clearDraftsForTab(tabId)` then close
- **Browser refresh** ŌåÆ draft lost (acceptable; `beforeunload` shows warning if dirty)

